{"tid":389250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李佳芯與「野獸」男友同居試婚 陳炳銓靠真誠冧掂女神","createTime":"2017-09-06T05:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T14:01:53.000Z","uid":32938,"like":212,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3fc1a68bdc12c0b41f1548b00498e72d0c0d7d0","tid":389250,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3eSEKDR2jv9SE6YtvCrvgg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170905f162802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3eSEKDR2jv9SE6YtvCrvgg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170905f162802.jpg&h=344ac309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】34歲的無線花旦李佳芯去年開始上位，更憑靚樣加演技榮升新一代「宅男女神」，其感情生活亦備受注視，更被踢爆與其貌不揚的ViuTV奀星陳炳銓拍拖，兩人還被網民喻為現代版的「美女與野獸」。雖然有指李佳芯被公司高層「照肺」，惟有轉玩地下情，但隨著女方逐漸坐穩女一之位，她亦冇有怕愈愛愈高調。<br />\n<br />\n最新一期《東周刊》指李佳芯與男友已發展到於將軍澳同居試婚，近日又甜蜜拍拖到西貢市中心行街，襯晒著白衫情侶裝，為愛巢添置廚具和糧食。另外，陳炳銓接受訪問時承認，與女友相處舒服自然又簡單，自稱沒有特殊魅力，相信是以真誠成功冧掂李佳芯；他又慶幸女友講心唔講金，亦不注重顏值。"},{"pid":"2f457a0cc32cda6d597fdef32e2f387776a40133","tid":389250,"uid":23878,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"係真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986614ddceb0f47bcbb0735ec62db145e0d4f37c","tid":389250,"uid":99805,"like":7,"dislike":184,"score":-177,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:51:56.000Z","msg":"其貌不揚但係又野獸,白粉班友進修下中文先啦"},{"pid":"bbff663f533fe7cd1202f1a2ed64f178f27e15fb","tid":389250,"uid":20302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"個樣成個av男優"},{"pid":"f0a2c1c89341eb79c540f3dd6031c95fe6ac444a","tid":389250,"uid":65587,"like":241,"dislike":2,"score":239,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:52:55.000Z","msg":"佢前世係咪救咗地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji